---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Blog posts and updates from Zaheed Ahmed Bhuiyan.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Personal Blog</p>
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p>
      Updates, reflections, and selected experiences from my academic journey,
      research activities, teaching work, and life at Towson University.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="blog-grid">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
      <article class="blog-card reveal">
        <p class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read post →</a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>